tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE community_policing_initiatives (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  initiative_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  location TEXT,
  officer_id INT,
  outcome TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE CommunityPolicingInitiatives (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    effectiveness_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE PoliceOfficers (
    officer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    officer_name VARCHAR(255),
    department VARCHAR(255),
    rank VARCHAR(50),
    years_of_service INT
);

CREATE TABLE community_policing_initiatives (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE policing_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    officer_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE initiative_evaluation (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_id INT,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    effectiveness_rating INT,
    comments TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE community_policing_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE police_officers (
    officer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    officer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    badge_number INT NOT NULL,
    rank VARCHAR(50),
    department_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE community_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    address VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    email VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE evaluations (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    officer_id INT,
    date DATE,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE police_officers (
    officer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    officer_name VARCHAR(255),
    badge_number INT,
    rank VARCHAR(50),
    center_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (center_id) REFERENCES community_centers(center_id)
);

CREATE TABLE community_events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    event_name VARCHAR(255),
    event_date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    center_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (center_id) REFERENCES community_centers(center_id)
);

CREATE TABLE incidents (
    incident_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    incident_type VARCHAR(50),
    incident_date TIMESTAMP,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    officer_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (officer_id) REFERENCES police_officers(officer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE evaluations (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    officer_id INT,
    officer_evaluation VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (officer_id) REFERENCES police_officers(officer_id)
);
